@startuml
title Shared Ollama Lifecycle State Machine

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> Unmounted

Unmounted : VHDX not mounted
Unmounted : Ollama stopped/disabled
Unmounted : New sessions refused

Unmounted --> MountedDisabled : VHDX mounted

MountedDisabled : model data available
MountedDisabled : control directory available
MountedDisabled : Ollama disabled

MountedDisabled --> Running : user starts shared Ollama\nremove draining\nmark enabled\nstart service

Running : accept sessions
Running : active leases may exist
Running : sockets may be ESTAB/SYN-RECV

Running --> Draining : stop requested\nor idle cleanup begins

Draining : refuse new sessions
Draining : wait for no live leases
Draining : wait for no ESTAB/SYN-RECV sockets
Draining : require stable clean checks

Draining --> MountedDisabled : safe stop\nstop service\ndisable service

Running --> EmergencyStop : VHDX disappears
Draining --> EmergencyStop : VHDX disappears
MountedDisabled --> Unmounted : VHDX dismounted

EmergencyStop : fail closed
EmergencyStop : stop Ollama
EmergencyStop : disable Ollama
EmergencyStop : refuse sessions
EmergencyStop --> Unmounted : cleanup complete

@enduml
